# __Live-Chat__
## Live Chat application
![](data:image/png;base64,)

## Project includes 12 parts
1. Folder checklist: Save results of product review according to list and task check (work of team members)
2. Folder customer-supplied: Save the customer documentation provided
3. Folder design: Save the project design document
4. Folder guideline: Save the project's documentation
5. Folder meetingminutes: Save minutes of group meetings
6. Folder plan: Save the project schedule and schedule
7. Folder q & a (Question and answer): Save Q&A list
8. Folder review: Save the product of review activities
9. Folder reference: Save the project reference
10. Folder report: Save the project report
11. Folder requirment: Save documents required by the project
12. Folder test: Save the test document, review
